 <!-- Branding -->
	
  <TorannMagic.TMAbilityDef ParentName="BaseMagicAbility">
    <defName>TM_Branding</defName>
    <label>Branding</label>
    <uiIconPath>UI/branding</uiIconPath>
    <description>Branding is used to create a temporary, magical mark on a pawn in order to create a link between the caster and the marked pawn. Brands can be both beneficial or detremental to the marked, depending on the type of brand used. Multiple brands may be placed on a single pawn as long as each brand is a different type. A caster may create as many brands as they wish, but each brand subtracts from the energy regeneration of the caster. Brands will be dispelled if the caster runs out of mana. Brands are a unique type of spell, and each brand must be learned seperately. Skill in branding affects all types of brands.</description>
    <manaCost>0</manaCost>
	<efficiencyReductionPercent>.1</efficiencyReductionPercent>
	<upkeepEfficiencyPercent>.03</upkeepEfficiencyPercent>
	<canCopy>false</canCopy>
	<shouldInitialize>false</shouldInitialize>
